 be given a free hand: Your Holiness shall see the work I will do and the account I will give of myself.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"570d5100-cefd-4d3e-9c21-788f542542dc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":4,"end":4,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"e10dc4fc-c6b0-4e9f-a812-0769683b94e8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":54,"end":54,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"c0d27cee-0e8b-4960-9e19-2ef82910d4f9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":89,"end":89,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"9a610626-1b48-445b-90a5-1c0ba93b5ed2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":104,"end":109,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"mysel","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"5c7d59c9-cc23-4478-af97-4d0abc65dfcf","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":116,"end":128,"value":"56a66a9e-ca50-45be-b8aa-aef2d47b5d96","text":"Your Holines","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a1bf49b7-e0e0-454b-b0f9-a7e50eefa083","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":160,"end":160,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"4f2db9f7-f389-4684-bcd5-4a2e71251347","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":226,"end":228,"value":"56a66a9e-ca50-45be-b8aa-aef2d47b5d96","text":"yo","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"1512b82e-819c-45c7-b617-c4bcb56863a2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":235,"end":235,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a4b0535e-2ded-4868-a458-21efff2da18b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":287,"end":287,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"cc744a45-0573-418f-b7a1-b